docs {
  ## Get Library Summary

  Returns per-library coverage statistics. No parameters required.

  **Expected Response:**
  Array of objects, each with:
  - `LibraryId` / `LibraryName`
  - `TotalItems` — total movies/episodes in library
  - `WithIntro` / `WithCredits` / `WithBoth` / `WithNeither` — counts
  - `ContentType` — "series", "movies", or "mixed"

  **Acceptance Criteria:**
  - ✅ Returns array (may be empty if no sync has run)
  - ✅ Each entry has library name and coverage counts
  - ✅ Requires admin authentication
}
